	(text "IO — badge_hw_design.md §Buttons, §SAO, §Connectors.\nButtons → GND with RP2040 internal pullups. SAO 2×3 standard pinout.\nmicroSD on SPI0 (SCK=GP2, MOSI=GP3, MISO=GP4, CS=GP5).\n4.7k I2C pullups for SAO bus (RP2040 internal pulls are too weak)."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 25 25 0)
		(effects
